title: Josefus - Dead Man (1970)
description:
***Note***  I have no idea which version of the CD this came from.

The short review below was pulled randomly from rateyourmusic.com


Balls to the wall acid fuzzy hard rock from Texas. These guys kickass and take names. Glorious bluesy psychedelic hard rock from the early 70's with very good guitar and an attitude that is raw. That shit is rarely caught on a recording. It is on this one.
